43:36.140 --> 43:38.350
Yeah, don't act so surprised.
You're really pretty.

43:40.810 --> 43:42.200
- That's very good of you.
- Beer, dad?

43:42.220 --> 43:44.310
Yeah. Yeah, thanks, bud.

43:47.610 --> 43:49.940
- Oh, great!
- Oh, my God!

43:50.020 --> 43:52.360
Amber Spear.

43:52.440 --> 43:54.990
