44:06.920 --> 44:08.460
Absolutely.

44:11.550 --> 44:13.130
Why not?

44:13.220 --> 44:16.930
I love this so much.
I really do.

44:17.010 --> 44:20.220
- That was so good.
- Josie, thank you.

44:20.300 --> 44:21.870
It was the classiest
roast chicken I ever had.

44:21.890 --> 44:25.060
Oh, wow.

44:25.140 --> 44:27.190
- Goodnight.
- Goodnight.

44:27.270 --> 44:29.360
- Goodnight.
- Goodnight.

44:31.650 --> 44:33.420
Oh, since I'm gonna be staying
in Magdalene a while,

44:33.440 --> 44:36.490
I'm gonna need a car, I thought
you might know someone.

44:36.570 --> 44:38.860
Yeah, of course. You just
let me know when you're ready.

44:38.950 --> 44:41.030
I'll be there.

45:02.180 --> 45:04.270
Josephine!

45:04.720 --> 45:08.350
Josie.

45:08.440 --> 45:09.770
Hey.

45:09.860 --> 45:10.940
