workout clothes.

45:22.700 --> 45:25.040
Well, Amber went
on a fitness kick last year

45:25.120 --> 45:27.960
and, uh, there's the results.

45:28.040 --> 45:30.120
They're yours now.
Have at it.

45:41.090 --> 45:43.180
You're up, slick.

45:44.390 --> 45:48.350
