of women.

45:48.440 --> 45:50.770
- Not in heels.
- Also, not in heels.

45:50.850 --> 45:51.870
When are you not in heels?

45:51.900 --> 45:53.150
Well, this morning when I

45:53.230 --> 45:55.480
