45:55.570 --> 45:57.650
Come on, let's see it.

46:00.070 --> 46:02.280
Back at it.

46:02.360 --> 46:04.620
- Oh, I feel silly!
- Stop it.

46:04.700 --> 46:07.120
You are nothing but class,
head to toe.

46:07.200 --> 46:09.080
You're just little bit
of a klutz.

46:09.160 --> 46:11.120
But you own it, baby,
'cause it's cute.

46:11.210 --> 46:12.890
