should put a glove to that face.

46:43.820 --> 46:47.200
- Name's Micky.
- Josephine.

46:47.280 --> 46:50.870
Please tell me Jake is opening
the gym to aerobics classes

46:50.960 --> 46:52.330
and you're the instructor.

46:52.420 --> 46:57.040
Oh, alas! I have to dash
your dream!

46:57.130 --> 46:59.960
Did you lose something, Mick?

47:00.050 --> 47:02.430
She's with me.

47:02.510 --> 47:03.870
Comin' to the match
Saturday night?

47:03.930 --> 47:05.260
What's up?

47:05.340 --> 47:07.390
Mick and I are in the league
together.

47:07.470 --> 47:09.640
I'll drop off tickets
at the box office for ya.

47:09.720 --> 47:11.040
Oh, you know what,
if she wants to come,

47:11.060 --> 47:12.520
I think I can handle it.

47:12.600 --> 47:14.560
You got three kids and DeeDee
to handle.

47:14.650 --> 47:16.560
I'll take her, okay?

47:16.650 --> 47:18.210
DeeDee's been gone
for five months, Mick,

47:18.230 --> 47:20.900
but I kinda feel like
you knew that.

47:20.990 --> 47:23.070
Right.

47:25.490 --> 47:28.990
We are gonna make cream puffs
from scratch.

47:29.080 --> 47:31.410
- Awesome!
- Hey, wait up.

47:31.500 --> 47:34.620
- Cream puffs, dude!
- Awesome, little dude.

47:34.710 --> 47:36.630
- Hi, Connor.
- Yo, Josie. You doing good?

47:36.710 --> 47:39.670
- I'm great. How are you?
- Nothing gets me down.

47:39.760 --> 47:41.800
