but I gotta clock in.

47:41.880 --> 47:43.840
Later, bro!

47:43.920 --> 47:46.550
You know they got cream puffs
at the bakery.

47:46.640 --> 47:48.220
But I bet yours will be better.

47:48.300 --> 47:50.220
Well, people sometimes
put sweet, whipped cream

47:50.310 --> 47:52.350
or vanilla pudding
between the choux pastry

47:52.430 --> 47:55.020
which can be exasperating.

47:55.100 --> 47:57.360
We are gonna make
creme patissiere.

47:57.440 --> 47:59.780
What's creme patissiere?

47:59.860 --> 48:01.940
Proof there is a God.

48:07.780 --> 48:09.870
Yo!

48:11.450 --> 48:13.410
Hey, Micky.

48:13.500 --> 48:16.290
Wanna check out the firehouse,
little man?

48:16.370 --> 48:18.460
I'll look after your bags,
you go in.

48:21.300 --> 48:23.840
Um, I'm supposed to be in charge
of Ethan, I kinda need to

48:23.920 --> 48:25.130
keep an eye on him.

48:25.220 --> 48:27.590
Yo, Jimbo!
My boy, Eth's in there!

48:27.680 --> 48:31.060
- Keep an eye on him, will you?
- Alright, I got him.

48:31.140 --> 48:32.810
You have plans tomorrow night?

48:32.890 --> 48:35.680
